  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Yurkovich","meanings":["Ukrainian (standard transliteration <b>Yurkovych</b>) and Belorussian: patronymic from the personal name   Yurko   and its Belorussian equivalent <i>Yurka</i>, pet forms of Ukrainian <i>Yuriy</i> and Belorussian <i>Yuray</i>, equivalents of Greek <i>Geōrgios</i> (see   George  ).","Americanized form of Croatian <b>Jurković</b>, Slovak and Slovenian <b>Jurkovič</b> (see   Jurkovic  , compare   Jurkovich   and   Yurkovic  ).","Jewish (from Bessarabia): habitational name for someone from Yurkovtsy in Ukraine."]},{"name":"Yorke","meanings":["English: variant of   York  ."]},{"name":"Yorks","meanings":["English: variant of   York  ."]}]},{"name":"Petronilla","type":"FIRST","meanings":["An old female name; an Italian diminutive formed from Pietro, i.e. Peter."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Petronilla de York was born in 1240, in Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Sir William de Gouvis in 1265, in Somerset, England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1240–":"1240–Surnud","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","1265–1290":"1265–1290","1240–Female":"1240–Surnud","1265":"1265","1240":"1240","1290":"1290","Somerset, England":"Somerset, England","Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Le Brook, Ilchester, Somerset, England":"Ilchester, Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1240–":"1240–Kuollut","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","1265–1290":"1265–1290","1240–Female":"1240–Kuollut","1265":"1265","1240":"1240","1290":"1290","Somerset, England":"Somerset, England","Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Le Brook, Ilchester, Somerset, England":"Ilchester, Somerset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1240–":"1240–Décédée","1240–Male":"1240–Décédé","1265–1290":"1265–1290","1240–Female":"1240–Décédée","1265":"1265","1240":"1240","1290":"1290","Somerset, England":"Somerset, Angleterre","Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"E